1 Information obtained shall not be published or be open for public inspection, except
2 to public employees in the performance of their duties, but any interested party at a
3 hearing before the secretary or his or her duly authorized representative shall be
4 supplied with information from such records to the extent necessary for the proper
5 presentation of his or her case.
